### 1. Abonelik oluştur — test receiver'a gönder
POST http://localhost:5155/api/webhook/subscribe
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "eventType": "order.created",
  "targetUrl": "http://localhost:5155/api/webhook/receiver"
}

### 2. Tüm abonelikleri listele
GET http://localhost:5155/api/webhook/subscriptions
Accept: application/json

### 3. Event tetikle — abonelere gönderilir
POST http://localhost:5155/api/webhook/trigger
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "eventType": "order.created",
  "payload": {
    "orderId": 123,
    "customerName": "Ahmet Yılmaz",
    "totalAmount": 299.99
  }
}

### 4. Gönderim loglarını gör
GET http://localhost:5155/api/webhook/deliveries
Accept: application/json

### 5. Aboneliği iptal et
DELETE http://localhost:5155/api/webhook/1